                        <p style="margin: 0;">It’s part of your job! DOE and Berkeley Lab policy require that all materials published by Berkeley Lab researchers as part of their employment at the Berkeley Lab or produced by using Berkeley Lab resources be submitted to DOE OSTI and made freely available to the public at no charge.</p>
