                        <p style="margin: 0;">The LBNL Publication Management System is an automated system administered by the <a href="http://www.cdlib.org/">California Digital Library</a> on behalf of LBNL in order to facilitate compliance with our OA policy. The system finds potentially relevant publications, presents them to authors for verification, stores bibliographic data and open access publications, and forwards them to OSI as required.</p>
